Using the SP1-Commercial Electric Smart Plug custom skill, you can now ask Alexa to turn your smart plug on and off. With SP1-Commercial Electric smart plug custom skill, you can make the electric appliances connected to the plug be on/off as you want. 

Steps to use SP1-Commercial Electric Smart Plug with Alexa:
1. Download “SP1-Commercial Electric Smart Plug” app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
2. Create an account and connect the device on the app;
3. Search “SP1-Commercial Electric Smart Plug” skill on Alexa, tap “ENABLE TO USE”;
4. Log in your account on Alexa and wait for Alexa to discover your devices;
5. Try to voice control SP1-Commercial Electric Smart Plug.

Here are some examples of the voice commands:

- Alexa, turn on the dining room plug
- Alexa, turn off the dining room plug

Any problems, please contact us at customer_care@homedepot.com
